sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant OP as Operator
    participant CLI as deepview memory acquire remote<br/>--transport dma-tb
    participant G as Safety Gates
    participant P as ThunderboltDMAProvider
    participant LC as leechcore (PCILeech)
    participant EB as EventBus

    OP->>CLI: --enable-dma --confirm<br/>--authorization-statement "..."
    CLI->>G: confirm present?
    CLI->>G: --enable-dma present?
    CLI->>G: euid == 0 (root)?
    alt any check fails
        G-->>CLI: AuthorizationError
        CLI-->>OP: abort
    end

    CLI->>P: build_remote_provider("dma-tb", endpoint, ctx)
    P->>EB: publish RemoteAcquisitionProgressEvent<br/>stage="iommu-check"
    P->>P: probe IOMMU status (VT-d / AMD-Vi)
    alt IOMMU active
        Note over P: log warning: DMA likely blocked;<br/>proceed anyway
    end

    P->>LC: init device, query memory map
    loop chunked read 0..max_bytes
        P->>LC: read(addr, chunk_size)
        LC-->>P: bytes
        P->>P: stream to output
        P->>EB: publish RemoteAcquisitionProgressEvent<br/>stage="stream"
    end

    P->>EB: publish RemoteAcquisitionCompletedEvent
    P-->>CLI: AcquisitionResult
    CLI-->>OP: success
